init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The first Dad to be ranked "#1 Dad" is a man named John.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is a loving and devoted father.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He has a simple job and is a devoted husband.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: John is suddenly the most famous man in the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: John is a simple man and does not know how to handle all of the attention.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: John goes to the town where he lives and meets with the other dads.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He asks them if they know anything about this.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: John decides to go to the town where the mug maker lives.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He wants to find out why his mug has stayed at #1 and why the other mugs have been changing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She wanted to give John a special gift.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: John is surprised to hear this.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He does not want to be the most famous man in the world.
